<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT5">
<l>tokutta varattaṉāyt tōlātāṉ mārvam</l>
<l>vakirtta vaḷaiyukirttōḷ mālē yukattil</l>
<l>orunāṉṟu nīyuyartti yuḷvāṅki nīyē</l>
<l>yarunāṉku māṉā yaṟi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Māl with shoulders [and] curved nails that tore open</l>
<l>the chest of the unvanquished [Hiraṇyakaśipu], who added boons [for himself]!</l>
<l>Know that You Yourself are the four rare [kinds of life]</l>
<l>by lifting [the worlds] up one day [after] drawing [them] in</l>
<l rend="indent">[at the end of] the yugas!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
